<font color="#FF0000">THANKS</font><br>
<tt>Mon Apr  7 19:51:44 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
Marc, thank you for your honestly and insight. It is heartening to see that all of our requests have engendered a response.  It is a pleasure to deal with honesty.  I respect and thank all at P.O.V. for all that has kept this site available for as long as it has been.  I think I really knew that at some time this would discontinue.  It was disappointment that caused me to vent.  I really knew that this site wasn't a &quot;freebie&quot;, that someone was paying the bills.  I sincerely want to thank all of those who supported, encouraged and helped this site as long they did.  It showed that somebody cared what we thought and what we had to , finally, say.  This has shown that we are welcome and that we are home because people have listened to what I felt and said.
